				<section>
					<h2>Javascript in practice is a clusterfuck</h2>
					<ul>
						<li class="fragment">PURE Javascript is a nightmare.</li>
						<li class="fragment">The DOM is a nightmare.</li>
						<li class="fragment">Everyone writes their own flavour of Javascript.</li>
						<li class="fragment">You can't learn Javascript from a single source.</li>
						<li class="fragment">Javascript takes a long time to get good at.</li>
						<li class="fragment">Learn how Javascript works.</li>
						<li class="fragment">Learn different Javascript paradigms.</li>
						<li class="fragment">Adapt to whatever "best practice" your workplace requires.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

